      *
     C                     MOVE WORKER    WWWKCD  60
     C           WWWKCD    CHAINAM#PP311             49
     C           *IN49     IFEQ '0'
     C           R3SKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           R3SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     49
     C                     ENDIF
      *
